Q_DESC:
The nodes are deleted D times from the end of the given linked list. For example if the given Linked List is 5-10-15-20-25 and remove 2 nodes, then the Linked List becomes 5-10-15.
INPUT
First line contains the number of datas- N. Second line contains N integers(the given linked list).
Third line contains no. of nodes to be deleted.
OUTPUT
Display the Linked list.
